name: Running Out Of Space (CaylebLucas)
description:
Ludum Dare 42 Entry.

Made By 1 Person, Designed by a lovable Idiot and Art created by an angry artist who made a fully animated astronaut character that was dropped due to time constraints...

A game full of mini games. Complete each level before the screen shrinks to nothing. You are running out of space so best complete them quick.

Credits // Twitters

Developer: @CaylebLucas

Designer (Loveable Idiot): @Dec_GameDev

Art (Angry Artist): @MattWardART
